<P>A Mathematical Que&s;tion, Propounded by the VICEGERENT of the World; An&s;wered by the KING of GLORY. Enigmatically repre&s;ented, and Demon&s;tratively opened, By <HI>JOHN JOHNSON.</HI></P>
