<P><HI>LONDON:</HI> Printed. BOSTON; NEW-ENGLAND, Re-printed: And Sold by GREEN &amp; RUSSELL, at their Printing-Office in Queen-&s;treet; and by PHILIP FREEMAN at his Shop in Union-&s;treet. MDCCLXII.</P>
